Package: aigenflow
Title: R Framework for Language Models and Intelligent Agents
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-11-12
Authors@R: person(given = "Margar",
           family = "Harutyunyan",
	   role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mharu997@gmail.com")
Description: A comprehensive R framework for working with language models and 
    intelligent agents. This package provides tools for integrating with 
    language models (like OpenAI's GPT), managing conversations, performing 
    data analysis, and creating automated workflows. Features include a 
    modular architecture for language model integration, conversation memory 
    management, extensible tool system, and chain-based workflow automation.
